dct_description_sm: Map of Tripoli showing the city beseiged by Spanish forces in 1510; relief shown pictorially. Historic Maps copy corresponds to copy described in "A Lafreri/IATO atlas" as: "State 2: with the title engraved just below the town, with the erasure of features behind the lettering ... The original lettering for the key remains, although the key is not present. cf. IM III, [554]."
